|Go|testing (built-in)|built-in + `-race`|testify/mock, mockery|testcontainers-go|rapid (built-in)|
|Rust|built-in `#[test]`|`#[tokio::test]`|mockall|testcontainers-rust|proptest|
|Java/Kotlin|JUnit 5|Awaitility|Mockito|Testcontainers|jqwik|
|C#|xUnit/NUnit|built-in async|NSubstitute|Testcontainers .NET|FsCheck|
|PHP|PHPUnit/Pest|—|Mockery|—|Eris|
|Elixir|ExUnit (built-in)|built-in|Mox|—|StreamData|

